# Success Metrics & KPIs Rules

## Purpose
Define measurable success criteria and monitoring framework for the product.

## Prerequisites
- Business objectives from MRD
- User stories and technical requirements defined

## Metrics Framework

### 1. North Star Metric Definition

```markdown
## North Star Metric
**Metric**: [Single most important metric]
**Definition**: [Precise calculation method]
**Current Baseline**: [If applicable]
**Target**: [6 month, 12 month, 24 month targets]
**Rationale**: [Why this metric matters most]
```

