#### Business Metrics
```markdown
## Business KPIs

### Revenue Metrics
- **MRR/ARR**: [Monthly/Annual Recurring Revenue]
  - Target: [Value]
  - Measurement: [Method]
- **ARPU**: [Average Revenue Per User]
  - Target: [Value]
  - Calculation: [Formula]
