#### Product Metrics
```markdown
## Product KPIs

### Adoption Metrics
- **Activation Rate**: [% users who complete key action]
  - Definition: [Specific action]
  - Target: [X%]
  - Timeframe: [Within Y days]
- **Feature Adoption**: [Per feature usage]
  - Priority Features: [List]
  - Target Adoption: [X% in Y time]

### Engagement Metrics
- **DAU/MAU**: [Daily/Monthly Active Users ratio]
  - Target: [X%]
  - Calculation: [Method]
- **Session Duration**: [Average time]
  - Target: [X minutes]
  - Segments: [By user type]
- **Actions per Session**: [Key actions]
  - Target: [X actions]
  - Actions Tracked: [List]

### Retention Metrics
- **Day 1/7/30 Retention**: [Cohort retention]
  - Targets: [X%, Y%, Z%]
  - Cohort Definition: [Criteria]
- **Churn Rate**: [Monthly/Annual]
  - Target: [<X%]
  - Segments: [By plan/persona]
```

