### Quality Metrics
- **Bug Escape Rate**: [Bugs found post-release]
  - Target: [<X per release]
- **Test Coverage**: [Code coverage percentage]
  - Target: [X%]
  - Types: [Unit, Integration, E2E]
- **Technical Debt**: [Measurement approach]
  - Target: [<X% of velocity]
```

